      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_mna_01_01/sud_vo_adv_card_mna_01_01-koh001.m4a",
      "text": "……まだ来ない。今日こそ、ヤバいか？\n電話するか――あ",
      "translations": {
        "en": "It’s almost time. Is she gonna be late?\nGuess I should make a call… Oh.",
