        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_schoolclass-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "stage01",
      "startTime": 9.933333333333334
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "mna",
      "speakerName": "長瀬麻奈",
      "speakerNameEn": "Mana",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-mana.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_mna_01_01/sud_vo_adv_card_mna_01_01-mna001.m4a",
      "text": "はぁ、はぁ、ま、間に合った～っ……！\nおはよ、はぁはぁ、{user}、くん……",
      "translations": {
        "en": "*huff* *huff* I-I made it…\nMorning… *huff* *huff* {user}…",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 14.9,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_schoolclass-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "stage01",
      "startTime": 14.9
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_schoolclass-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "stage01",
      "startTime": 19.4
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "speakerNameEn": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-makino.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_mna_01_01/sud_vo_adv_card_mna_01_01-koh002.m4a",
      "text": "おはよう\n挨拶は息を整えてからでいいよ",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Morning.\nNo rush‚ take a moment‚ catch your breath.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 20.6,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "mna",
      "speakerName": "長瀬麻奈",
      "speakerNameEn": "Mana",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-mana.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_mna_01_01/sud_vo_adv_card_mna_01_01-mna002.m4a",
      "text": "今日は油断して二度寝しちゃった～\n琴乃もお母さんも、起こしてくれないんだもん",
      "translations": {
        "en": "I let my guard down and overslept!\nKotono and mom didn’t wake me up…",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 26.5,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_schoolclass-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "stage01",
      "startTime": 30.6333333333333
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "mna",
      "speakerName": "長瀬麻奈",
      "speakerNameEn": "Mana",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-mana.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_mna_01_01/sud_vo_adv_card_mna_01_01-mna003.m4a",
      "text": "まぁ、朝からのダッシュで\nいい運動にはなったけどね",
      "translations": {
        "en": "So I had to run.\nWell‚ I guess it was good exercise.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 33.03333333333333,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_schoolclass-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "stage01",
      "startTime": 35.3666666666667
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "speakerNameEn": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-makino.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_mna_01_01/sud_vo_adv_card_mna_01_01-koh003.m4a",
      "text": "だいぶ疲れてるみたいだな\nやっぱり、最近仕事入れ過ぎじゃないのか",
      "translations": {
        "en": "You look tired.\nAren’t you working a little too much lately?",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 38.233333333333334,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "speakerNameEn": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-makino.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_mna_01_01/sud_vo_adv_card_mna_01_01-koh004.m4a",
      "text": "少し減らすか？\n体を壊したら元も子もないし……",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Maybe we should cut things back a little.\nYour health is important…",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 43.13333333333333,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_schoolclass-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "stage01",
      "startTime": 45.63333333333333
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "mna",
      "speakerName": "長瀬麻奈",
      "speakerNameEn": "Mana",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-mana.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_mna_01_01/sud_vo_adv_card_mna_01_01-mna004.m4a",
      "text": "何言ってるの、デビューしたばかりの新人アイドルが\n忙しいなんてありがたいことじゃん",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Oh‚ come on. A rookie idol like me who just had her debut\nshould be glad to be busy.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 49,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "mna",
      "speakerName": "長瀬麻奈",
      "speakerNameEn": "Mana",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-mana.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_mna_01_01/sud_vo_adv_card_mna_01_01-mna005.m4a",
      "text": "もっと入れたいぐらいだよ\n本当はこうして授業に出る時間も惜しいくらい",
      "translations": {
        "en": "The more work‚ the merrier.\nI wish I could take time out of school.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 53.46666666666667,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_schoolclass-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "stage01",
      "startTime": 56.7333333333333
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "speakerNameEn": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-makino.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_mna_01_01/sud_vo_adv_card_mna_01_01-koh005.m4a",
      "text": "俺も麻奈も学業優先だ\n三枝さんもそう言ってただろう？",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Both of us need to put school first.\nThat’s what Saegusa-san said.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 59.43333333333333,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "mna",
      "speakerName": "長瀬麻奈",
      "speakerNameEn": "Mana",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-mana.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_mna_01_01/sud_vo_adv_card_mna_01_01-mna006.m4a",
      "text": "分かってるよ、だから、頑張って\n両立してるんでしょ",
      "translations": {
        "en": "I know. That’s why I’m working hard\nto take care of things on both sides.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 64.36666666666667,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_schoolclass-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "stage01",
      "startTime": 66.4
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "mna",
      "speakerName": "長瀬麻奈",
      "speakerNameEn": "Mana",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-mana.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_mna_01_01/sud_vo_adv_card_mna_01_01-mna007.m4a",
      "text": "私、成績は落ちてないもん\n……あんまり",
      "translations": {
        "en": "I’m still getting the same grades as before.\n…Well‚ almost the same grades.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 69.46666666666667,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_schoolclass-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "stage01",
      "startTime": 70.76666666666667
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "speakerNameEn": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-makino.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_mna_01_01/sud_vo_adv_card_mna_01_01-koh006.m4a",
      "text": "成績はともかく、最近麻奈は遅刻ギリギリな日が\n多過ぎる。今日こそヤバいと思ってたんだぞ",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Putting grades aside for a second‚ you’ve been cutting it close lately.\nI thought you were going to be late today.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 74.43333333333334,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_schoolclass-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "stage01",
      "startTime": 78.5333333333333
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "mna",
      "speakerName": "長瀬麻奈",
      "speakerNameEn": "Mana",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-mana.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_mna_01_01/sud_vo_adv_card_mna_01_01-mna008.m4a",
      "text": "そう思うなら、毎朝、車で迎えに来てくれれば\nいいのに",
      "translations": {
        "en": "If that’s what you think‚ why don’t you drive me to school\nevery morning?",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 82.26666666666667,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "speakerNameEn": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-makino.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_mna_01_01/sud_vo_adv_card_mna_01_01-koh007.m4a",
      "text": "免許も車も持ってないよ……",
      "translations": {
        "en": "I don’t have a driving license… or a car…",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 83.6,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_schoolclass-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "stage01",
      "startTime": 86.36666666666666
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "mna",
      "speakerName": "長瀬麻奈",
      "speakerNameEn": "Mana",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-mana.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_mna_01_01/sud_vo_adv_card_mna_01_01-mna009.m4a",
      "text": "取ればいいのに。もう取れるんでしょ？",
      "translations": {
        "en": "You’re eligible to take the driving exam‚ aren’t you?",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 86.36666666666666,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "mna",
      "speakerName": "長瀬麻奈",
      "speakerNameEn": "Mana",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-mana.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_mna_01_01/sud_vo_adv_card_mna_01_01-mna010.m4a",
      "text": "{user}くんが車の運転出来たら便利だし\n一緒にいろんな所に行けて楽しいだろうな",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Just imagine how convenient it would be if you could drive.\nWe could go to all sorts of places together.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 92.03333333333333,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "speakerNameEn": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-makino.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_mna_01_01/sud_vo_adv_card_mna_01_01-koh008.m4a",
      "text": "俺だって学校とマネージャー業務の両立で\n今はいっぱいいっぱいだ",
      "translations": {
        "en": "I’m balancing school and my work as manager too.\nI’ve got plenty on my plate.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 98.36666666666666,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_schoolclass-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "stage01",
      "startTime": 100.53333333333333
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "mna",
      "speakerName": "長瀬麻奈",
      "speakerNameEn": "Mana",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-mana.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_mna_01_01/sud_vo_adv_card_mna_01_01-mna011.m4a",
      "text": "え～？　そこは頑張ってよ。マネージャー",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Aww‚ come on! You’ve got this‚ manager.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 100.53333333333333,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "speakerNameEn": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-makino.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_mna_01_01/sud_vo_adv_card_mna_01_01-koh009.m4a",
      "text": "ああ、もしずっと麻奈のマネージャーを\n続けるなら必要だしな……",
      "translations": {
        "en": "I guess I would need it at some point‚\nif I’m gonna continue as your manager…",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 108.16666666666667,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_schoolclass-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "stage01",
      "startTime": 111
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "mna",
      "speakerName": "長瀬麻奈",
      "speakerNameEn": "Mana",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-mana.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_mna_01_01/sud_vo_adv_card_mna_01_01-mna012.m4a",
      "text": "何それ。もしかしたら、いつか\n私のマネージャー辞めるつもり？",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Are you saying that you’re\nplanning to quit as my manager?",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 113.56666666666666,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_schoolclass-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "stage01",
      "startTime": 116.2
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "mna",
      "speakerName": "長瀬麻奈",
      "speakerNameEn": "Mana",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-mana.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_mna_01_01/sud_vo_adv_card_mna_01_01-mna013.m4a",
      "text": "厳しい芸能界に、か弱い女の子を一人残して\n去っていくの？　酷いよ、{user}くん！",
      "translations": {
        "en": "You’ll leave a young‚ helpless girl out there\nto fend for herself in the tough world of show business?",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 120.76666666666667,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_schoolclass-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "stage01",
      "startTime": 125.333333333333
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "mna",
      "speakerName": "長瀬麻奈",
      "speakerNameEn": "Mana",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-mana.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_mna_01_01/sud_vo_adv_card_mna_01_01-mna014.m4a",
      "text": "お願い、私を捨てないで！",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Don’t abandon me! I beg you!",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 125.33333333333333,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "speakerNameEn": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-makino.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_mna_01_01/sud_vo_adv_card_mna_01_01-koh010.m4a",
      "text": "お、おい、誤解を招く言い方はよしてくれ……",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Wait‚ you know that’s not what I meant…",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 129.63333333333333,
      "sfxList": [
        {
          "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBgm/sud_se_adv_gaya-02.m4a",
          "delay": 0,
          "startTime": 129.63333333333333
        }
      ]
    },
    {
